
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Image Search Abstraction Layer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="header">
      Image Search Abstraction Layer
    </h1>
    <blockquote>
      User stories:
      <ul><li>I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.</ul>
      <ul><li>I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.</ul>
      <ul><li>I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.</ul>
    </blockquote>
    <h3>Example creation usage:</h3>
    <h4>To see latest image searches...</h4>
    <code>https://fcc-imagesearch-soham1.c9users.io/api/latest/imagesearch</code>
    <br>
    <h4>To see image search results...</h4>
    <code>https://fcc-imagesearch-soham1.c9users.io/api/imagesearch/*searchtext*</code>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
